    "title": "Hollywood stars who have Indian spiritual gurus",
    "text": "Dec 29, 2023, 01:11 PM IST Julia Roberts She has publicly talked about her admiration for Hindu guru Neem Karoli Baba and his teachings. Roberts credited him for inspiring her spiritual journey. Richard Gere Known for his interest in Buddhism, Gere has been associated with the Dalai Lama and is a fervent supporter of Tibetan causes. Demi Moore Demi Moore's visited Mcleodganj in 2013 with spiritual teacher Hargopal Kaur Khalsa. She had also shared a photo with spiritual figure Mata Amritanandamayi, also known as Amma on Mother's Day. Russell Brand The comedian and actor had mentioned his admiration for various spiritual teachers, including Paramahansa Yogananda and Swami Vivekananda. Will Smith Will Smith has been seen attending and endorsing Sadhguru's events and teachings, expressing admiration for his wisdom. Natalie Portman Natalie Portman, an Academy Award-winning actress, has shown interest in mindfulness, meditation, and Eastern philosophies. While not explicitly stated, she has been spotted at events where Sadhguru was a speaker.",
